room_title: Escape room "Silent Night" by Solve Entertainment in Duluth
room_description:
Detectives! You have been assigned to investigate the recently discovered lair of Mycroft, a madman who has placed four bombs across the city and rigged them to blow at midnight. It is now 11pm and you have 60 minutes to save your city. The clues to the bombs locations, and possibly even their disarm codes, are somewhere in this room. Can you find them in time?
Save the city, or sleep in heavenly peaceâ€¦
